  "texts": [
    "This database is refined from a broader collection through keyword-based search, with the selected documents undergoing text embeddings for efficient storage and retrieval (1).",
    "The framework is further augmented with a suite of medical tools, including specialized web search capabilities through platforms such as Google, PubMed and access to the OncoKB API.",
    "The agent's capabilities are further expanded through the integration of a vision model tailored for generating detailed reports from CT and MRI scans, alongside MedSAM, a stateof-the-art medical image segmentation model and access to a simple calculator.",
    "Article https://doi.org/10.1038/s43018-025-00991-6 Stage 2: RAG + response generation Question Clinical Context FFig. 3 |3Fig.",
